{"tid":1561769,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港 時代革命 香港人要守護我哋既自治權","createTime":"2019-09-11T17:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T17:14:35.000Z","uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cfba9a4fc44c2849b66b68309672050cc85c7a36","tid":1561769,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"五夜講場 - 歷史係咁話 2018：自古牢獄不通風<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1hCtPnw7BzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1hCtPnw7BzQ&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okXocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=4b94fb66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1hCtPnw7BzQ</a><br />\n<br />\n話說小弟一方面貼文宣,上街遊行;另一方面吸收不同學者既研究知識<br />\n希望能幫助推動目前既時代革命<br />\n有幸睇到上面呢個節目<br />\n節目提到我哋現在擁有既法治,權利都喺係中英聯合聲明後先開始建立<br />\n而在此之前既港英統治並冇上一輩吹既咁好,同目前中共想對我哋統戰可以話係一樣<br />\n當然呢樣就要問返上一輩點解要咁吹,佢哋北望神洲就吹香港好勁,佢哋對住我哋有幸生於法治確立既時代就吹以往既香港好美好<br />\n但原來喺佢哋心目中,喺事實中,港英並唔係一個好既統治<br />\n所以以上節目希望能讓大家明白<br />\n<br />\n我哋既要對抗中共既強壓統治,亦無需重提港英既鉗制<br />\n我哋要做既喺 光復香港 重奪香港人由法治人權確立開始努拼搏返嚟既光輝<br />\n我哋要做既喺 時代革命 認清香港同中共,同大英,同世界既關係,開創香港自治既先河<br />\n<br />\n手足們,約定煲底見"},{"pid":"f06a3a13db38ffb622ace73cb7bfafd6748cc7c8","tid":1561769,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:14:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s